OL,3,CMan arrested following Carrickfergus
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a stabbing
OL,8,Fin Carrickfergus.
OL,10,FPolice said the victim was stabbed in
OL,11,Fthe chest and suffered head injuries
OL,12,Fin the Rodgers Quay area around 7.30pm
OL,13,Fon Wednesday.
OL,15,FIt is understood to have happened
OL,16,Fduring a motorcycle event.
OL,18,FPolice said a male suspect reportedly
OL,19,Ffled the scene following the
OL,20,Faltercation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
