OL,3,CMan arrested following Carrickfergus
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the incident
OL,7,Farrested a 41-year-old man on Saturday.
OL,9,FThe PSNI said: "A man has been
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,11,Fmurder and possession of an offensive
OL,12,Fweapon, following a search in the
OL,13,FNewtownabbey area on Saturday May 30.
OL,15,F"He has been taken into custody and
OL,16,Fwill be interviewed in due course."
